.TH MOT2BIN 1 "2026-05-18" "f9dasm 1.83" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
mot2bin \- convert Motorola S\-record files to a raw binary file
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B mot2bin
.RI [ \-out
.IR file ]
.I file.s19
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B mot2bin
reads a Motorola S\-record (S19/S28/S37) file and writes the decoded data
as a raw binary stream.
.PP
It is shipped as a companion utility to
.BR f9dasm (1)
for preparing raw binary input from common ROM dump formats.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BI \-out " file"
Write the binary output to
.IR file
instead of standard output.
.SH EXAMPLES
Convert
.I rom.s19
to
.IR rom.bin :
.IP
.B mot2bin \-out rom.bin rom.s19
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR f9dasm (1),
.BR hex2bin (1),
.BR cmd2mot (1)
.SH AUTHORS
Part of the
.B f9dasm
suite by Arto Salmi, Hermann Seib, Colin Bourassa, and Rainer Buchty.
